---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 零基础自动驾驶学习系统
description: 从数学、数据与深度学习开始，构建面向自动驾驶数据实习生的可验收学习路线。
permalink: /index.html
bodyClass: portal-body textbook-home-body
homePage: true
---
{% from "partials/course-card.njk" import courseCard with context %}
{% set pilotCourseCount = curriculum.courses | countStatus('pilot') %}
{% set legacyCourseCount = curriculum.courses | countStatus('legacy') %}
{% set availableCourseCount = pilotCourseCount + legacyCourseCount %}
{% set startCourse = curriculum.courses | courseById('math-diagnostic') %}

<div class="textbook-home-shell" id="top">
  <aside class="home-chapter-nav" id="chapters" aria-labelledby="catalog-title">
    <p class="home-catalog-kicker">Learning map · {{ curriculum.courses.length }} courses</p>
    <h2 class="home-catalog-title" id="catalog-title">学习目录</h2>
    <ol class="home-catalog-list">
      {% for stage in curriculum.stages %}
      {% set stageCourses = curriculum.courses | coursesForStage(stage.id) %}
      <li{% if loop.first %} class="is-active"{% endif %}>
        <a class="home-chapter-link" href="#stage-{{ stage.id }}">
          <span class="home-chapter-code">{{ stage.code }}</span>
          <span class="home-chapter-name">{{ stage.title }}</span>
          <span class="home-chapter-count">0{{ stageCourses.length }}</span>
        </a>
        {% if loop.first %}
        <ol class="home-subchapter-list" aria-label="{{ stage.title }}课程">
          {% for course in stageCourses %}
          {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ course.url | siteUrl }}"{% if loop.first %} aria-current="step"{% endif %}>
              0{{ course.order }} {{ course.title }}
            </a>
          </li>
          {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
    <div class="home-catalog-foot">
      <strong>不用按目录硬学</strong>
      <p>目录是地图，不是任务清单。遇到真实任务时，从最相关的一章进入就好。</p>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <section class="home-hero-paper" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
    <p class="home-crumb">首页 <span>/</span> 起点导航 <span>/</span> 第一步</p>
    <p class="home-eyebrow">写给第一次接触自动驾驶数据的你</p>
    <h1 id="hero-title">不会没关系，<br>我们从第一步开始</h1>
    <p class="home-hero-intro">看到矩阵、坐标系、nuScenes 或神经网络会发懵，很正常。这里先用生活里的画面讲明白，再看公式、手算一个例子，最后才运行代码。</p>
    <div class="home-continue-row">
      <a class="home-primary-action" data-continue-link href="{{ startCourse.url | siteUrl }}">继续上次学习</a>
      <span class="home-resume-meta"><strong>默认从“数学起点导航”开始</strong>已经学过时，会自动接回上次的位置</span>
    </div>

    <p class="home-entry-label">或者，按你此刻的情况进入：</p>
    <nav class="home-entry-list" id="start-here" aria-label="按当前情况选择起点">
      <a class="home-entry" href="{{ '/guide.html' | siteUrl }}">
        <span class="home-entry-number">01</span><strong>第一次来</strong><small>先花 5 分钟认识怎么学</small>
      </a>
      <a class="home-entry" href="{{ '/notes/nuscenes-dataset.html' | siteUrl }}">
        <span class="home-entry-number">02</span><strong>接到 nuScenes 数据任务</strong><small>先听懂数据集在说什么</small>
      </a>
      <a class="home-entry" href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">
        <span class="home-entry-number">03</span><strong>一看到公式就发懵</strong><small>只补眼前真正缺的基础</small>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </section>

  <aside class="home-today-note" id="today" aria-labelledby="today-title">
    <span class="home-note-label">Today · 一次只学一点</span>
    <h2 id="today-title">今天只做<br>一件事</h2>
    <p class="home-today-lead">不是“学会数学”，只是找到现在卡住你的那个符号。</p>
    <div class="home-one-task">
      <span>当前小任务</span>
      <strong>用自己的话说出：函数到底是在做什么？</strong>
      <p>先猜，再看解释。猜错不会扣分。</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="home-status-list" aria-label="当前学习状态">
      <li><span>当前阶段</span><strong>P0 · 起点</strong></li>
      <li><span>可学习课程</span><strong>{{ availableCourseCount }} 门</strong></li>
      <li><span>我的进度</span><strong data-progress-summary>还没有开始也没关系</strong></li>
    </ul>
    <a class="home-learning-card-link" href="{{ '/update.html' | siteUrl }}">
      <span>My learning card</span>
      <strong>记下我刚刚理解的东西 →</strong>
    </a>
    <a class="home-stuck-link" href="{{ '/guide.html#stuck' | siteUrl }}">卡住了？先看这里，不用自己硬撑 →</a>
    <p class="home-encouragement">“不知道”也是一个有效答案，它会告诉我们下一步该去哪。</p>
  </aside>

  <section class="home-learning-loop" id="learning-loop" aria-labelledby="loop-title">
    <div class="home-loop-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="home-section-kicker">First-principles learning loop</p>
        <h2 id="loop-title">每一课，都按同一条路走</h2>
      </div>
      <p>不要求第一遍记住全部。先建立直觉，再让公式和代码替你检查理解。</p>
    </div>
    <ol class="home-loop-list">
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 01</span><strong>说清问题</strong><small>今天只弄懂一件事</small></li>
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 02</span><strong>先猜一下</strong><small>猜错没关系，要说理由</small></li>
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 03</span><strong>看图建直觉</strong><small>先看方向、远近与变化</small></li>
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 04</span><strong>翻译公式</strong><small>每个符号都换成人话</small></li>
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 05</span><strong>算一个例子</strong><small>先手算，再运行代码</small></li>
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 06</span><strong>故意改错</strong><small>找出假设与失败边界</small></li>
      <li><span class="home-step-number">Step 07</span><strong>讲给别人</strong><small>换个条件，再独立解释</small></li>
    </ol>
    <a class="home-loop-guide" href="{{ '/guide.html' | siteUrl }}">看一个完整示范：一小时怎样学完一小节 →</a>
  </section>

  <div class="home-lower-content">
    <section class="portal-section home-milestones" id="milestones">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">学一点，就能开始帮上忙</p>
        <h2>能力会一段一段长出来</h2>
        <p>不必等所有课程学完。先完成一个能交付的小任务，再把缺少的知识补回来。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid three">
        <article class="panel"><span class="milestone-label">先走 25–40 小时</span><h3>能帮忙整理数据</h3><p>看懂目录和文件格式，做基础统计，把结果画出来，并说明自己检查了什么。</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><span class="milestone-label">继续到 80–120 小时</span><h3>能独立完成一个小任务</h3><p>理解坐标、标定和场景切分，完成一份 nuScenes mini 数据报告。</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><span class="milestone-label">完成核心路线后</span><h3>能解释一次模型实验</h3><p>运行小型 PyTorch 训练，读懂曲线，找出失败样本，而不只是说“代码跑通了”。</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="v2-stats course-overview-stats" aria-label="课程体系规模">
      <div><strong>{{ curriculum.stages.length }}</strong><span>个阶段，按需要进入</span></div>
      <div><strong>{{ curriculum.courses.length }}</strong><span>门课，不要求一次学完</span></div>
      <div><strong>3</strong><span>门数学核心课，从直觉开始</span></div>
      <div><strong>1</strong><span>份最后能讲清楚的作品</span></div>
    </div>

    <section class="portal-section" id="learning-path">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="section-kicker">完整课程地图</p>
        <h2>课很多，但每次只决定“下一门”</h2>
        <p>“可以开始”表示页面会一步步带你学；“可以阅读”表示知识已经完整；“正在准备”只是提前告诉你以后会学什么。</p>
      </div>
      <nav class="stage-nav" aria-label="学习阶段快捷导航">
        {% for stage in curriculum.stages %}<a href="#stage-{{ stage.id }}">{{ stage.code }} {{ stage.title }}</a>{% endfor %}
      </nav>
      <ol class="stage-list">
        {% for stage in curriculum.stages %}
        {% set stageCourses = curriculum.courses | coursesForStage(stage.id) %}
        <li class="learning-stage" id="stage-{{ stage.id }}">
          <div class="stage-summary">
            <span class="stage-number">{{ stage.code }}</span>
            <h3>{{ stage.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ stage.description }}</p>
            <p class="stage-time">大约需要 {{ stage.effort }}</p>
            <div class="stage-gate"><strong>学到这里，你应该能：</strong>{{ stage.gate }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="course-grid">{% for course in stageCourses %}{{ courseCard(course) }}{% endfor %}</div>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="portal-cta" aria-labelledby="start-title">
      <div><p class="section-kicker">不知道选哪门时</p><h2 id="start-title">先看看你适合从哪里开始</h2><p>不会的题直接写“不知道”。这不是考试，只是帮你找到下一小步。</p></div>
      <div class="hero-actions"><a class="button" href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">带我做第一步</a></div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
